			<change xml:lang="EN">
				<p sameAs="title">Request letter from Vitorino José, farmer, to Jacinto Gomes.</p>
				<p sameAs="summary">The author asks the recipient to deliver certain cows to the bearer, to which he refers as being "emparcadas", saying that later he will compensate him for these services.</p>
				<p sameAs="settingDesc">Vitorino José has been accused of stealing some cattle from captain Américo. He has tried to incriminate another man, José Morgado, but later his declarations involved some contradictions. He ended up in prison and paid his penalty.</p>
				<p sameAs="text">To Mr. Jacinto Gomes.</p></change>
